65
00:04:46,130 --> 00:04:48,900
There's a dinosaur here. Right over there!

66
00:04:50,370 --> 00:04:52,430
Let's go and get it together. Okay?

67
00:04:53,510 --> 00:04:54,970
Come on, a little more...

68
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:58,140
Mom will help you.

69
00:04:58,140 --> 00:05:00,910
This will be a happy memory for the two of us.

70
00:05:00,910 --> 00:05:03,250
Let's take good care of it together.

71
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:07,490
I'm tired. I'm sleepy...

72
00:05:07,490 --> 00:05:10,520
No, no! Do your best. I'll help you!

73
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:12,960
Your friend is here too.

74
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:17,600
We're all in this together.
Let's all find happiness together.

75
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,030
Okay.

76
00:05:19,630 --> 00:05:23,230
A little further...
A little more, and you'll reach our happiness.

77
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,880
There! You got it!

78
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:32,710
I did it!

79
00:05:34,910 --> 00:05:37,820
It's my birthday present to you.

80
00:05:37,820 --> 00:05:40,890
I haven't been able to give you one
since the day we met,

81
00:05:40,890 --> 00:05:42,690
but will you accept one now?

82
00:05:42,690 --> 00:05:44,360
Yes. I'm so happy.

83
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:47,620
You are? Isn't it nice, Misuzu?

84
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:49,330
It's so cute.

85
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:51,300
He says, "Gao!"

86
00:05:51,300 --> 00:05:52,460
Gao...

87
00:05:53,030 --> 00:05:55,470
Dear gods, I offer my thanks.

88
00:06:04,580 --> 00:06:06,100
Mom...

89
00:06:06,710 --> 00:06:10,910
She hasn't slept... because of me.

90
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:15,120
Oh, dear. I was asleep, wasn't I?

91
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,290
I'm sorry.

92
00:06:16,290 --> 00:06:20,750
It's okay. Let's go to sleep.
I want to sleep with you, Mom.

93
00:06:20,990 --> 00:06:23,200
What should I do?

94
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:26,600
If you go to sleep and dream,
your pains will get worse, won't they?

95
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,570
No. There's no pain now.

96
00:06:28,570 --> 00:06:29,470
What?

97
00:06:29,470 --> 00:06:32,440
There's been no pain for a while now.

98
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,960
I wonder why...

99
00:06:34,140 --> 00:06:37,180
Really? You really don't feel any pain?

100
00:06:37,180 --> 00:06:41,510
That's why I want to sleep.
I want to sleep lots and get better.

101
00:06:41,610 --> 00:06:42,980
Really?

102
00:06:43,180 --> 00:06:46,550
I'm so glad! It's really great, isn't it, Misuzu?

103
00:06:46,550 --> 00:06:48,850
You were trying so hard, weren't you?

104
00:06:48,850 --> 00:06:51,350
You were rewarded, Misuzu!

105
00:06:54,460 --> 00:07:00,300
Misuzu... no... That's not candy...

106
00:07:00,300 --> 00:07:03,100
You mustn't eat it...

107
