Isn't your body sore?

116
00:07:37,970 --> 00:07:39,940
Do you remember who I am?

117
00:07:40,370 --> 00:07:42,570
Mom! Good morning!

118
00:07:46,850 --> 00:07:50,750
It's cleared up nicely,
now that the storm's passed.

119
00:07:50,750 --> 00:07:54,050
Mom, I had another dream last night.

120
00:07:54,420 --> 00:07:55,620
A dream?

121
00:07:55,620 --> 00:07:58,490
You always get worse after a dream.

122
00:07:58,490 --> 00:08:01,360
I'm fine. I have no pains anywhere.

123
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:04,760
Besides, that was my last dream.

124
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:10,570
Really? You're really all right?
You don't feel any pain anywhere?

125
00:08:10,570 --> 00:08:11,570
I'm fine.

126
00:08:11,570 --> 00:08:12,430
V!

127
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:14,210
Really?

128
00:08:14,210 --> 00:08:18,240
That freeloader said something about
after your last dream...

129
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:20,710
But I guess he was wrong.

130
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:23,880
I was so worried.

131
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:28,750
