a dinosaur with wings.

137
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:53,650
He was flying like he really
enjoyed it, saying, "Gao!"

138
00:08:53,650 --> 00:08:54,710
Is that right?

139
00:08:54,710 --> 00:08:59,810
And I was flying above him.
I was looking back over my shoulder.

140
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:06,330
I had wings. I was flying with pure white wings.

141
00:09:06,330 --> 00:09:08,920
Is that so? What a nice dream.

142
00:09:09,330 --> 00:09:12,430
No, it was a sad dream.

143
00:09:12,430 --> 00:09:15,130
The world's saddest dream.

144
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:19,370
But you know, that was my last dream.

145
00:09:19,370 --> 00:09:22,740
From now on I will stay with you.

146
00:09:22,740 --> 00:09:25,270
Forever and always...

