206
00:11:49,990 --> 00:11:52,220
You'll be my goal, Mom.

207
00:11:52,220 --> 00:11:55,190
I see. So I'm the goal?

208
00:11:55,930 --> 00:11:58,660
Yes. You and Sky are my goal.

209
00:11:59,130 --> 00:12:01,730
Just take it slowly. I'll wait as long as you need.

210
00:12:01,730 --> 00:12:02,470
Okay.

211
00:12:02,470 --> 00:12:03,840
Are you all right?

212
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:05,960
Yeah! V!

213
00:12:06,670 --> 00:12:07,970
V...

214
00:12:09,740 --> 00:12:12,400
Over here, Misuzu. I'm over here.

215
00:12:13,210 --> 00:12:15,610
That's right. Just take it slowly.

216
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:18,780
If you try really hard, I'm sure you'll get well.

217
00:12:18,780 --> 00:12:21,750
We'll do our best together. Right, Misuzu?

218
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:25,190
It's all right, isn't it?

219
00:12:25,190 --> 00:12:26,590
Huh? What is?

220
00:12:26,590 --> 00:12:29,530
I've done my best, haven't I?

221
00:12:29,530 --> 00:12:31,800
It's okay to cross the goal line, isn't it?

222
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,330
Are you tired already?

223
00:12:33,330 --> 00:12:37,000
Okay, when you reach your goal,
we'll go home and play cards.

224
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,670
No...

225
00:12:38,670 --> 00:12:42,500
My goal... The goal I've been trying
to reach all this time...

226
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:43,740
Huh?

227
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:48,140
I did my best, so it's okay, isn't it?

228
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:51,450
I can rest now, can't I?

229
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:55,290
Don't tell me you're in pain?
Have you been in pain?

230
00:12:55,290 --> 00:12:56,650
Don't move!

231
00:12:59,590 --> 00:13:02,360
It's not true. Tell me it's not true!

232
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:05,130
You're going to get better, aren't you?

233
00:13:05,130 --> 00:13:07,100
The bad dreams are supposed to be over, right?

234
00:13:07,570 --> 00:13:09,600
I'm sorry, Mom.

235
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:13,940
But I was able to do all that I needed to.

236
00:13:13,940 --> 00:13:16,110
That's why, I'm going to cross the goal line.

237
00:13:16,110 --> 00:13:20,350
No, Misuzu. You mustn't come here.
You mustn't cross the goal line!

238
00:13:20,350 --> 00:13:25,010
We just started! Why, we just started yesterday!

239
00:13:25,420 --> 00:13:26,990
We're going to get it all back.

240
00:13:26,990 --> 00:13:30,320
The happy life that we should have started
ten years ago.

241
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:33,260
We're going to get that all back together!

242
00:13:33,260 --> 00:13:36,560
Our happiness just started!

243
00:13:36,560 --> 00:13:41,230
No, we did everything.
Almost more than enough.

244
00:13:41,230 --> 00:13:45,100
This summer was filled with enough
happiness for a lifetime.

245
00:13:45,100 --> 00:13:49,110
No! You're wrong! There are lots
of things I want to do!

246
00:13:49,110 --> 00:13:52,340
I love you, Misuzu. There are lots
of things I want to do with you!

247
00:13:52,340 --> 00:13:54,480
Everything is just beginning!

248
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:58,850
This summer, I decided I would try
one more time.

249
00:13:58,850 --> 00:14:02,840
My summer started on the day I met Yukito.

250
00:14:03,390 --> 00:14:08,690
All sorts of things happened;
painful things, difficult things...

251
00:14:08,690 --> 00:14:11,990
But I'm glad I tried so hard.

252
00:14:12,230 --> 00:14:16,070
My goal was the same as my happiness.

253
00:14:16,070 --> 00:14:18,400
I wasn't all alone.

254
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:22,910
That's why... That's why
I'm going to cross the goal line.

255
00:14:22,910 --> 00:14:24,910
No! We've only started!

256
00:14:24,910 --> 00:14:26,670
We've only started, I tell you!

257
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:35,710
Goal!

258
00:14:37,790 --> 00:14:52,430
Ano umi doko made mo aokatta tooku made
The sea was blue into the far distance

259
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:55,740
